Type: Package
Package: FlyDreamR
Title: Infer Sleep/Wake States from activity data using hidden Markov
    models (HMMs)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Arijit", "Ghosh", , "arijitghosh2009@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7910-3170"))
Description: Implements an iterative hidden Markov model for
    inferring sleep and wake states from activity-count data, plus tools
    for data preparation, visualization, and summary metrics.
